					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Performance Monitoring</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400">Real-time metrics, query performance, and resource usage monitoring.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Secure by Default</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400">Encrypted connections, automatic security updates, and isolated environments.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Easy Scaling</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400">Scale your database resources up or down with a single click.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Direct Access</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400">Connect with standard tools. Full SQL access and admin privileges.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-gray-800/50 border border-gray-700">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">99.9% Uptime</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400">High availability with automatic failover and redundancy.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<div class="text-center p-12 rounded-2xl bg-primary">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Deploy Your Database?</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-6">Get started in minutes. No credit card required.</p>
			<a href="/register" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-primary font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all hover:bg-gray-100">
				<span>Create Free Account</span>
				<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
				</svg>
			</a>
